quran[5{c,v,t}:
9,32,yeh log chahtay hain ke Allah ki roshni ko apni phoonko se bujha den magar Allah apni roshni ko mukammal kiye baghair maan-ne wala nahi hai khuwa kafiroon ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho
9,33,woh Allah hi hai jis ne apne rasool ko hadaayat aur deen haq ke sath bheja hai taakay usay poori jins deen par ghalib kar day khuwa mushrikon ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho
9,34,"ae imaan laane walo, inn ahal kitaab ke aksar ulama aur darwaishoo-n ka haal yeh hai ke woh logon ke maal baatil tareeqon se khatay hain aur inhen Allah ki raah se roktay hain dard naak saza ki khush khaberi do un ko jo sonay aur chandi jama kar ke rakhtay hain aur inhen khuda ki raah mein kharch nahi karte"
9,35,"aik din aeye ga ke isi sonay chandi par jahannum ki aag dehkai jaye gi aur phir isi se un logon ki pishanyon aur pehluo aur pithon ko dagha jaye ga yeh hai woh khazana jo tum ne apne liye jama kya tha, lau ab apni smiti hui doulat ka maza chako"
9,36,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke mahino ki tadaad jab se Allah ne aasman o zameen ko peda kya hai Allah ke noshte mein baara hi hai, aur un mein se chaar mahinay haraam hain yahi theek zabita hai lehaza un chaar mahino mein apne oopar zulm nah karo aur mushrikon se sab mil kar lrho jis terhan woh sab mil kar tum se lartay hain aur jaan rakho ke Allah Muttaqiyun hi ke sath hai"
